// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1395 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 56911f58-718c-51cf-ab7a-b9204aed5fac

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
